yllables.", "usage": "strongman accusations", "safetyNotes": "Booming projection should not clip TTS output. Compress for mobile."}, {"id": "voice_werewolf", "kind": "voice", "prompt": "A snarl layered under calm, controlled speech. Think of an animal tamer commanding a beast while the beast is inside them. The growl emerges on R-sounds. French, restrained predator.", "usage": "werewolf night phase and disguised debate lines", "safetyNotes": "Growl effect must be subtle enough for TTS not to garble words."}], "codeStubs": [{"path": "src/generated/circus-werewolf/roles.ts", "purpose": "Role definitions with voice asset mappings.", "content": "export const roleVoiceMap: Record<string, string> = {
